Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.33,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.73,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I was on my way to pick up \Nthe uniform I ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.79,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}but I couldn't find the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.79,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:53.59,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}so I've been wandering around all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.69,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,The croquette place by the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:53.84,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all here together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.14,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, guys, are you okay with me \Ncalling you by your first names?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.54,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing now, Sakai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:01.30,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'd like if it you all called \Nme by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:01:59.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Probably going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.30,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,You were singing, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.47,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Uien, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.68,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Nein! It's {\i1}Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.55,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ween.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:07.85,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.54,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were singing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ween!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.36,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wien, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.33,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It all sounds the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.87,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san, go show Wien around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.51,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:18.99,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wien?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.93,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san, will you come \Nover to my house for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:23.80,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:29.37,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\NGathering and Struggling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.90,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa! Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.14,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Aloha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.66,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Shiho-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.48,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Heading to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.82,Default,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. She your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.74,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Sakai Wakana-san. \NShe's in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.38,Default,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, you girls have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.97,Default,Shino,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back by dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Aloha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.78,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Your older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:08.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,My mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Sabure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta eat a lot, so \Nyou can grow up big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.76,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.59,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.18,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.97,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She's my pet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.97,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.63,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.92,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.66,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the moldy smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:32.48,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.86,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,So, Okita-san, is this temple your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.02,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.13,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,And you can call me Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.16,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Epic Failure] Joint High School Recital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.11,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.00,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a recording of last year's recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.23,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She was so nervous, she couldn't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:05.80,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I laughed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.65,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you were too nervous to actually sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:14.48,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,you could've just lip-synched
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.86,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,until it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.23,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The end result was a huge failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.49,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,but I like what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.15,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me laugh, every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.22,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.42,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakai-san, can we put your \Nname down for the new choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want this to \Nbe her last time singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.34,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,so she's been practicing hard all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:49.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how slight her chances, \NI want to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:49.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.73,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We need at least five \Npeople to start a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to actually participate, \Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:59.19,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Push too hard, and she'll \Njust get mad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.78,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,If you just need my name, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.15,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.12,Default,Bag,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shimada Clothing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.14,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are pretty complex, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.45,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,And they wear the weirdest \Noutfits on our days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.88,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.65,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna grab some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.45,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's just me \Nand my sister at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.61,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no one around \Nto cook a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.55,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.30,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Could this possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.78,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thinly-sliced meat, cooked with vegetables \Nin a light-but-savory sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,A bastion of Japanese cuisine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.91,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This is none other than sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.03,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.69,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, let's eat, and then \Nwe'll go buy you a better book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.75,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get your little \Nbrother to make his friends join?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.20,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! Motion accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.81,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,The dancing violinist Kumagai \NTetsuji will be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.21,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,so you could try to recruit people \Nwho'd join because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.17,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.17,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He has a very weird style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:07.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! And we could get Shiho-san \Nto make us some flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.28,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You know she's going to \Ngo completely overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.15,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:15.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,My mom gets asked to make \Nillustrations and flyers all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Well, her drawings really pack a punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.66,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Quit doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to invite your \Nfriends to join my choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.38,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:40.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Moving your porn stash to a \Nnew hiding spot won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.58,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:49.59,Default,Poster,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choir Club \NJoin the Choir Club \Nand meet Kumagai Tetsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.08,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.59,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting a new choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.71,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Have a flyer. It's for our choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:58.81,Default,Makoto,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.06,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:07.35,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the announcement \Nat the next board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.89,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.90,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.03,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.55,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.81,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem with the \Ncurrent choir program?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not allowed to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.78,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough members,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.19,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,and it won't be like the other choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I want to perform at the recital \Nwith a completely new concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll create a big—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.26,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the vice principal \Nhas her own ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.78,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Performing at the joint recital \Nwith a random group is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.12,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Club Application\NChoir Club \NSakai Wakana\NInvited by a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.69,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,This could be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:12.57,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,It might also be a good incentive for some \Nof the top hitters in the music program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.09,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Would I be acceptable as advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.10,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I have always had faith in the \Npotential of my young students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.77,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of man I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Mwah! Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.75,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Very interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.60,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:11.77,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.93,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Each and every arrow is important, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.41,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,When does the new choir club start up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, during lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.12,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,So, I want to choose our song right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but looking at sheet music \Nisn't giving me any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I also can't choose a song that only I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:39.21,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hoping to have a song \Nwe could start practicing tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You can play piano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.60,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mandatory part \Nof the music curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.11,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I'm not as good \Nas the piano majors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san, I know we said you'd \Nbe a member in name only,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but could you help us out the next \Ntwo days, while we choose a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.29,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What about the actual recital, \Nand your rehearsals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's asking a friend of his, \Nwho plays the electone, as we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to pick a song and start \Npracticing, as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.71,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.18,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.33,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Two cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.80,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,One is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.59,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,All right, can you play \Nthrough these in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to get the \Nfeel of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Start with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of strange, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,There are scribbles all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:31.06,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard it before, \Nand the music was even written by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I like this song. It reminds \Nme of the Condor Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:03.02,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,They're a pretty old band. \NI'll lend you one of their CDs some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:03.98,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.58,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This song might work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Play it again, right from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.27,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Melody of the Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.42,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.54,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no objections,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.18,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,this is the song I'd like us \Nto perform at the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.88,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,What time will rehearsals start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I've got cram school, \Nso I can't stay too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.69,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.57,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you all submit the times \Nthat are good for you to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.34,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.97,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The recital's coming up fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:09.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll rehearse as hard as we \Ncan, so we can blow them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.59,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}35th Joint Recital
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I got the principal's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:23.94,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.08,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,What are you singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.98,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow you to sing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.33,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to select something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:45.82,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a song you can \Nsing for the fun of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.55,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's new to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:56.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but it's like I can feel how much \Nthe composer enjoyed writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.40,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's very straightforward and sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:03.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell the composer loves to \Nsing, and yet there's also joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it incorporates \Neverything I'm feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I want to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.23,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoying something and \Nbringing joy are different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.48,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You are incapable of bringing \Nthose two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:35.64,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fresh wind races through \Nthe grass and leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:42.99,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view is clear, \Nas far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:49.16,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, a graceful light is flooding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:04.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.25,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is the principal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. And nobody's heard from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.74,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone else drive us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.66,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have anyone supervising you, \Nyou'll need to go back to your classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.26,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,"Participation in club activities \Nwithout an advisor's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.60,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,or assistant advisor's \Nsupervision is prohibited."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:25.37,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,As club president, I'm \Nsure you know this rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.77,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your assistant advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.21,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to get in touch with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.44,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Since you'll need to stay here with \Nyour club to await further news,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.31,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to appoint someone to lead \Nthe afternoon rehearsal in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.42,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.93,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.80,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sakai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.68,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,She said you're the only one who can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:07.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote down everyone's \Nparts and their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The music is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if you have any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know how things \Nare going on our side, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.40,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Two cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.90,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takahashi isn't answering. \NI'll go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.88,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.49,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If the principal shows up, \Npick me up on the way with the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:57.99,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:15:59.65,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.23,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of Tomoko's students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.15,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.23,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,She just went to the \Nhospital for a check-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.23,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me which hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I found the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You "found" him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:27.71,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Joint Recital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.71,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Rehearsal's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.58,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:33.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,They just found the principal, \Nbut I'm not sure what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.02,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirohamazaka High School Choir Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with Mr. Tada...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:35.64,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.54,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.66,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.35,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I stopped, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.61,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,And I just had it waxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:54.13,Default,Princ,0000,0000,0000,,I even wax my bicycles. That's \Nthe kind of man I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.49,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.24,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Maternity Ward
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.80,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.00,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Okita? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:10.50,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Are you pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.37,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The principal's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.27,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:19.33,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But I called the school and \Narranged for the bus to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,so I think we'll make it, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.90,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll go to the auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the hospital, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Konatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.27,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:36.69,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please let the \Nchoir club sing last?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.91,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're on their way \Nand will definitely make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.11,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's asking a lot to change \Nthe program last-minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.54,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a call from the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.46,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:51.36,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't want to, \NI'll put your club after the voice majors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.86,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.43,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.14,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,This is really cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:17:59.80,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.54,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rest of your group?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.99,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,On their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.31,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san's the only one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.88,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.67,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.91,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.33,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to crash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I've trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't going to be like last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:34.74,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next up, we have the Shirohamazaki High \NSchool Choir Club performing "Melody of the Heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.46,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Miyamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.38,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.38,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! They're introducing you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone else already out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.16,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.85,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally cleared the congestion, \Nso it shouldn't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.47,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.49,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.86,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.61,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them you're not going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:12.27,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You get all these people involved, \Nand now you just wanna quit and go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.42,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.59,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to overwrite last year's shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Singing is all that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.06,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I make a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I have to see this through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help, Sakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.20,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find the answer \Nyou wanted last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.78,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you sing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.80,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We've just gotta get through one song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.17,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.73,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine you're looking \Nat a pumpkin patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a pumpkin patch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.42,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,A watermelon patch, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:30.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:36.79,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.57,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I think I owe her three cakes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:53.27,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fresh wind races through the grass and leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:21:00.53,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view is clear, as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:07.57,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, a graceful light is flooding,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:15.58,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}softly illuminating everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:21.09,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you can't see the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.17,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because of the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:28.85,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the future you're dreaming of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.03,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is still right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:35.14,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's sing every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.79,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with all our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:42.83,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our song echoing to the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.51,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.63,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if it should ever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:53.31,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}reach you again somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:57.17,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:04.74,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the days we spent with beaming smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:18.83,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's sing every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:22.42,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with all our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:26.48,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our song echoing to the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:29.19,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:33.30,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if it should ever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:36.96,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}reach you again somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:40.83,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:47.63,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the days we spent with sparkling eyes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:55.66,Default,song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The days we spent with beaming smiles. \N
